$interpreted: Yan-Bo: Clues to the culprit, I do not find. If quick I am not, Karnulla will......
Yan-Bo: The child, how is he not here? Karnulla〜Karnulla!
Yan-Bo: Frogodile footprints!? Just one, I see not. This is what?
Yan-Bo: In this direction, they lead......
Karnulla: ......I can't accept. Get out of here! I can pretend I didn't see anything.
Yan-Bo: Karnulla!
Yan-Bo: So it was you!
Karnulla: No, it was them who did it. I had nothing to do with it......
Yan-Bo: Not only life, you have destroyed, but hanging with these scoundrels, you were!
Karnulla: No, I wasn't! They told me to go with them, but I...
Yan-Bo: Explain nothing, you can! Wasting my efforts, you have!
Karnulla: .........
Yan-Bo: In vain, my strict education has been. Think not, did I, that you——
Karnulla: ——Cut the crap, old man!
Karnulla: When it comes down to it, you always think that I'm gonna turned bad. That's why you never really believed in me!
Yan-Bo: No, I......
Karnulla: Whatever I want to do, you don't allow. I stick up for you, you yell at me!
Karnulla: No matter what I do, you're never happy!
Yan-Bo: Karnulla, mistaken, you are...
Karnulla: Every day, I meditate and train, and you know what? I hated it! But I still did it for you, and now you don't even believe my own words?
Karnulla: So that's how it's gonna be? Well, I won't take it anymore, Yan-Bo!
Yan-Bo: Karnulla, are you alright?
Karnulla: See? They are willing to protect me. That's what family is supposed to be!
Yan-Bo: Concerned for you, I am. Out of love, my training and education are......
Karnulla: Yeah right. You're always repressing my nature. You don't care about me. You only cared about making me into what you want me to be!
Yan-Bo: I......
Karnulla: And they told me that you and that nasty mermaid were the ones who drove them out of their habitat. Is that true?
Karnulla: Not saying anything, huh? Well, then I guess the answer's obvious.
Karnulla: We've spent so much time together and you don't even like me. Looks like this is where we go our separate ways.
Yan-Bo: Karnulla. Forgive me. My fault this is!
Karnulla: Stop following me. Since you took care of me for three years, I'll give you some time to get outta here.
Karnulla: From here on out, this will be our stronghold for the strengthening of the frogodile tribe!

Yan-Bo: ... And God, who lent the bud of love, 
Called back to Heaven his own; 
Death kissed it sleeping, and no more 
Its soft eyes on me shone...
Yan-Bo: So... in fact it was I, who let you down......
